    "As a result, pre-RS traceability is commonly applied only to fulfill regulatory compliance for safety-critical systems, without fully realizing the potential benefits, such as a transparent RS creation process that encourages exchange and avoids conflicts during requirement discussions.Although the challenges and benefits of pre-RS traceability are unique and significant, pre-RS traceability is commonly treated only as an afterthought to post-RS traceability.In this article, we document the state-of-the-art of pre-RS traceability by analyzing current problems, use cases, techniques, and tools.",
